title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1225.53 - Berth space may be cleared so as to permit closing of street side doors
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1225.53 - Berth space may be cleared so as to permit closing of street side doors

State Regulations

The superintendent may, at any time, order berth space
to be cleared so as to permit the closing of the doors on the street side of
the berth. Notes
